:["Feminine form of the old Roman family name   Julius .  A woman called Julia is mentioned in Paul's Epistle to the Romans (Romans 16:15), and the name was borne by numerous early saints. Its frequency increased with the vogue for classical names in the 18th century, and it continues to enjoy considerable popularity, although the recent introduction of   Julie   to the English-speaking world has reduced this somewhat. Well-known bearers include the British actress  Julia Foster  (  b. 1941 ) and American actress  Julia Roberts  (  b. 1967  as  Julie Fiona Roberts )."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Julia Liszewska was born in 1435, in Hungary. She had at least 1 son with Stanislau Boris. She died after 1455, in her hometown."},"et":{"1435–aft 1455":"1435–pärast 1455","1435–Male":"1435–Surnud","1455–Male":"1455–Surnud","1435–1455":"1435–1455","1435":"1435","1455":"1455","Abt 1455":"umbes 1455","aft 1455":"pärast 1455","Hungary":"Ungari","Buda, Budapest, Hungary":"Buda, Budapest, Ungari"},"fi":{"1435–aft 1455":"1435–1455 jälkeen","1435–Male":"1435–Kuollut","1455–Male":"1455–Kuollut","1435–1455":"1435–1455","1435":"1435","1455":"1455","Abt 1455":"noin 1455","aft 1455":"1455 jälkeen","Hungary":"Unkari","Buda, Budapest, Hungary":"Buda, Budapest, Unkari"},"fr":{"1435–aft 1455":"1435–après 1455","1435–Male":"1435–Décédé","1455–Male":"1455–Décédé","1435–1455":"1435–1455","1435":"1435","1455":"1455","Abt 1455":"environ 1455","aft 1455":"après 1455","Hungary":"Hongrie","Buda, Budapest, Hungary":"Buda, Budapest, Hongrie","lifeSummary":"Julia Liszewska est née en 1435, à Hongrie. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Stanislau Boris. Elle est décédée après 1455, dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"1435–aft 1455":"1435–nach 1455","1435–Male":"1435–Verstorben","1455–Male":"1455–Verstorben","1435–1455":"1435–1455","1435":"1435","1455":"1455","Abt 1455":"um 1455","aft 1455":"nach 1455","Hungary":"Ungarn","Buda, Budapest, Hungary":"Ofen, Budapest, Ungarn","lifeSummary":"Julia Liszewska wurde 1